<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fafafa;">
    <main style="text-align: center; padding: 50px 20px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;">Your Second Brain</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            An all-in-one Notion system to organize your tasks, projects, goals, notes, and references.
